{"tid":1680924,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唐詩詠認單身仲好珍惜洪永城","createTime":"2019-10-29T06:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T05:40:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"bba81ebee21f3136e48e4dd3fc509e8174d2e05e","tid":1680924,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:04:52.000Z","msg":"藝人唐詩詠昨午到中環出席活動，談到早前為好友黃翠如籌劃生日派對，她說：「佢有講明要叫邊個嘅。（難得同洪永城同場？）又唔係，平時你哋見唔到啫！（網民叫你哋復合？）唔好搞咁多嘢啦，我好珍惜呢段友情。」又斷言單身已一段日子，間接否認與緋聞男友陳思銘的關係。問到好友可有「好介紹」，她笑說：「如果有介紹，都要過咗黃翠如嗰關，佢會幫我篩選，而且嚴格兼有要求，你睇佢老公幾好就知。（怪唔得你冇拖拍！）我信佢，反而阿田（田蕊妮）就Open啲。」她坦言如今擇偶，希望盡量揀圈外人：「我拍拖想低調，但如果對方係圈內人好難，又會大壓力，比較難處理。」<br />\n活動上，唐詩詠戴上價值接近2億的珠寶，打趣指「身家過億」：「我第一對鑽石耳環係媽媽送嘅，平時冇特別買珠寶作收藏。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Xq7Yka7xg7DwyqmCSa0IGQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/c794e2ab644ad3d2ce6763fc006cef25\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXq7Yka7xg7DwyqmCSa0IGQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fc794e2ab644ad3d2ce6763fc006cef25&h=9b2c6713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%A0%E8%AA%8D%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%B2%E5%A5%BD%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B8%E5%9F%8E-214500162.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2594%2590%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E8%25A9%25A0%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E7%258F%258D%25E6%2583%259C%25E6%25B4%25AA%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E5%259F%258E-214500162.html&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=5ba7a85a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%A0%E8%AA%8D%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%B2%E5%A5%BD%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B8%E5%9F%8E-214500162.html</a>"},{"pid":"170a435204670a187383d493aeda536ffcbe804f","tid":1680924,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":2,"